entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`uid` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT NOT NULL, `fileName` TEXT NOT NULL, `isLocked` INTEGER NOT NULL)

contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_file_entity_fts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `file_entity` BEGIN DELETE FROM `file_entity_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_file_entity_fts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `file_entity` BEGIN DELETE FROM `file_entity_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_file_entity_fts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `file_entity` BEGIN INSERT INTO `file_entity_fts`(`docid`, `fileName`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`fileName`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_file_entity_fts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `file_entity` BEGIN INSERT INTO `file_entity_fts`(`docid`, `fileName`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`fileName`); END
entities.createSql: CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`fileName` TEXT NOT NULL, content=`file_entity`)
